price: 68. Too waqdi Yalli : Muusaw mameesitin diggah atu ama marak aysettooh iro raaqettok kaak inne.
arabic: قُلۡنَا لَا تَخَفۡ إِنَّكَ أَنتَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ

version.title: Afar translation
version.description: Translation of the Quran meanings into Afar by a group of scholars. under supervision of Shaikh Mahmud Abdulkader Hamza. 1441 H.

meta.transliteration: qul'nā lā takhaf innaka anta al-aʿlā
